{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/q1orytsv","slide":2,"text":"MyndMemory","textPreview":"MyndMemory","textChars":10,"textLines":1,"bbox":[146,51,220,28]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/1gvy90je","slide":2,"text":"THE PROBLEM","textPreview":"THE PROBLEM","textChars":11,"textLines":1,"bbox":[72,132,470,28]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/8z25kb6x","slide":2,"text":"AI apps forget too much context.","textPreview":"AI apps forget too much context.","textChars":32,"textLines":1,"bbox":[72,182,560,198]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/je9cvixc","slide":2,"text":"Agents can chat, but most products still treat memory as logs, prompts, or fragile retrieval glue.","textPreview":"Agents can chat, but most products still treat memory as logs, prompts, or fragile retrieval glue.","textChars":98,"textLines":1,"bbox":[74,424,510,112]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/qtcj6tov","slide":2,"text":"MyndMemory pitch deck","textPreview":"MyndMemory pitch deck","textChars":21,"textLines":1,"bbox":[72,672,260,22]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/xczed8v6","slide":2,"text":"02","textPreview":"02","textChars":2,"textLines":1,"bbox":[1165,668,42,24]}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/8v6psfil","slide":2,"bbox":[720,189,15,15]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/w3m94fu1","slide":2,"text":"Context is scattered","textPreview":"Context is scattered","textChars":20,"textLines":1,"bbox":[756,180,420,30]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/loj2t83i","slide":2,"text":"Important user state lives across events, documents, conversations, and app data.","textPreview":"Important user state lives across events, documents, conversations, and app data.","textChars":81,"textLines":1,"bbox":[756,214,420,42]}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/ex0nuxc3","slide":2,"bbox":[720,267,15,15]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/3itgfmlk","slide":2,"text":"Retrieval is not memory","textPreview":"Retrieval is not memory","textChars":23,"textLines":1,"bbox":[756,258,420,30]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/wb2hwfyx","slide":2,"text":"Search can return facts, but it does not decide what should be learned, updated, or forgotten.","textPreview":"Search can return facts, but it does not decide what should be learned, updated, or forgotten.","textChars":94,"textLines":1,"bbox":[756,292,420,42]}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/lwval87e","slide":2,"bbox":[720,345,15,15]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/e9cvixcz","slide":2,"text":"Builders lack a control plane","textPreview":"Builders lack a control plane","textChars":29,"textLines":1,"bbox":[756,336,420,30]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/3q5o7qpg","slide":2,"text":"Teams need a way to inspect and tune how agents remember across real workflows.","textPreview":"Teams need a way to inspect and tune how agents remember across real workflows.","textChars":79,"textLines":1,"bbox":[756,370,420,42]}
{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/8vuo2e","slide":2,"text":""}
