{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/lkjm1cfa","slide":7,"bbox":[720,189,15,15]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/d8v6psfi","slide":7,"text":"Framework, not one-off glue","textPreview":"Framework, not one-off glue","textChars":27,"textLines":1,"bbox":[756,180,420,30]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/onyd0z61","slide":7,"text":"A reusable memory runtime instead of bespoke prompt and retrieval code per app.","textPreview":"A reusable memory runtime instead of bespoke prompt and retrieval code per app.","textChars":79,"textLines":1,"bbox":[756,214,420,42]}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/z25kb6xk","slide":7,"bbox":[720,267,15,15]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/6hcrmhk3","slide":7,"text":"Inspectable by design","textPreview":"Inspectable by design","textChars":21,"textLines":1,"bbox":[756,258,420,30]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/dg7adsji","slide":7,"text":"Teams can see what the agent learned, why it recalled it, and how policies affected output.","textPreview":"Teams can see what the agent learned, why it recalled it, and how policies affected output.","textChars":91,"textLines":1,"bbox":[756,292,420,42]}
{"kind":"shape","id":"sh/ovahoza1","slide":7,"bbox":[720,345,15,15]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/vahoza1g","slide":7,"text":"Built for adaptive behavior","textPreview":"Built for adaptive behavior","textChars":27,"textLines":1,"bbox":[756,336,420,30]}
{"kind":"textbox","id":"sh/6tovahoz","slide":7,"text":"Memory can be strengthened, decayed, corrected, merged, or scoped across identities.","textPreview":"Memory can be strengthened, decayed, corrected, merged, or scoped across identities.","textChars":84,"textLines":1,"bbox":[756,370,420,42]}
